Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流行性？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳下腺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.39,0:00:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱作  流行性耳下腺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是常說的多福感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要休養一個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打針呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The spear is very break and hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it is large and long,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jurinsa thows it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahunture grabs it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As she pressing it against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she had never fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學美出院為止  學生會就只剩我和芽生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這些都要…整理啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說來  還從沒跟小芽單獨說過話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力和小芽愉快地聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回家的時候再一起吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:02.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾衣竿  賣晾衣竿了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒法辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得學美一不在就沒人起頭聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是神經太過緊繃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不好意思  明天壘球部還有體能訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是跟你談這些的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  只要適當地配合一下她的話題不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣的話題才算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看過的電視之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽好像不看電視的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近聽過的CD呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像喜歡聽古典的  我一點都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來她會笑話我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  找人幫忙的話去找小桃啊  去找小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經叫她了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道小芽就是這性格  跟她妥協一下也沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才剛進的學生會  心裡比你還沒底呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好對人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  囉哩吧嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  吃飯吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜…柑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（關門  請明天再來）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我今天有事不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊…是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  跟她交上朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問到甚麼隱私了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都在聊些甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭宣傳時的CG真的是衛藤同學做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  跟她單獨在一起一定很吃力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心裡比你還沒底呢  好好對人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要好好對她的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然  雖然用嘴說不上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要寫信  能有個開端的話  肯定能跟她拉近距離
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個  還真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你常來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏出第一步  踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  給學美寫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光香  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想去學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要遲到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  我今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了對了  有你的信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有郵戳  應該是直接放在郵箱裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就吃麵包吧  沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  光香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話給上原同學商量了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她建議我要不要寫寫信看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就寫了這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…其實我並不擅長跟人交談
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不是不想交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道該怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為甚麼昨天沒接電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道該怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻森同學你既溫柔  又開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要是能與你自由地交談該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會  要一起加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:56.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「給稻森同學  衛藤芽生」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一部分同學對學園祭是否會延期有所疑問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事哦  學園祭的準備活動才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會延期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會還有蜜柑和小芽在  大概沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你們這身衣服在哪裡買的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主題？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  在上次的學生總會上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所要展現的學園祭的大致概念  我們已經能瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  具體來說\N你們到底想要得到甚麼效果  該如何行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不事先定好方針的話  或許也會和去年一樣搞出個不知所謂的學園祭來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  「生機勃勃  令人興奮」這樣的不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  應該再具體一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說在體制上可以被承認的像樣點的說法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於全權交與學生負責的學園祭  有些老師也存在著不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖櫻可是歷史悠久  有優良傳統的學園哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在對天宮同學的做法不理解的教師  也並不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下島這個叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為下島老師是反對他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  要想一個讓我們提出他們反對方接受的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是那樣的嗎  下島？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…總之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管那回事  就我剛才說的主題是絕對需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己也要給自己定個指標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借這個機會認真的考慮一下也並不壞  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天宮出院後開始算起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…給你們一個星期時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這差不多能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…下島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人討論不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…學美…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學美回來之前  我們兩個人開始考慮主題不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老師他畢竟也是老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽取兩個人想出來的主題的話  也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家覺得我們是「隨意想出」的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「隨意想出」的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是兩個人嘗試想出的主題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小芽兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的…所以才說是「隨意想出」的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說哪一個作為主題都不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼會這樣欠缺靈感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  這些都太追求華麗反而過於籠統了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法令人覺得「生機勃勃  令人興奮」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話在比賽中可是贏不了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:14:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出氣勢來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感…感覺好像要想出甚麼來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  再跑一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT ON  FIGHT ON…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是…按照我們自己的方法來考慮吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊…贊成…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咽下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能忍住不吐出來真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:45.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（學美出院日！）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（風格與用語要統一  避開抽象以及曖昧的表現）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天要定下來！）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子…餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼亂來的話飯會燒糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣才不會燒糊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好飽好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給家裡打個電話說一聲行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡的人不擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣躺著的話  就能更好地看星星了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天宮學美  出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽同學說你們在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個文件是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱著我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小芽成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  又似乎成為了親密的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過學園祭  應該會和更多的人結成伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:39.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（從朋友到伙伴）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
